	<h1 class="title">冯唐的那根金线，在李银河手里捏着呢</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">托马斯骆</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-29 17:50:41 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19913/medium/19913.jpeg?1451376768" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


